me":"2020-10-16T20:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GoknSjx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoknSjx.png&h=9a6d27f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T22:25:12.000Z","msg":"腳背做咩？水腫？"},{"pid":"6b765a18c1718fcd81abe453b6ea5913c4587a7a","tid":2246144,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdYEbWR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdYEbWR.png&h=0fa12a05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c9b113f4aff9e752f66229b8d3fd7c0341643cf","tid":2246144,"uid":183058,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T02:48:48.000Z","msg":"常玉晚年鉅作「曲腿裸女」1.98億港元成交　破個人拍賣紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w68s5pG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw68s5pG.jpg&h=5544aafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳奇畫家常玉的晚年鉅作「曲腿裸女」，昨日在香港蘇富比（Sotheby's）現代藝術晚間拍賣會上，以大約1.98億港元（包括買家傭金）成交。<br />\n「曲腿裸女」由此超越2011年「五裸女」的1.28億港元，創下常玉個人作品的拍賣價新紀錄。而同場上拍的另兩件常玉作品也有不俗表現，1930年代作品《中國花布上的粉紅裸女》拍出4990.4萬港元，常玉中期花卉作品《盆花》則以4363.95萬港元成交。<br />\n<br />\n蘇富比官網介紹，《曲腿裸女》誕生於1965年4月，是常玉最後一件裸女作品，堪稱其人生終極鉅作。藝術家將大自然之雄奇造化寓於人體，亦將人類身體之美接引宇宙，以東方山水美學重新演繹西方經典，創寫曠世無雙之女性豐姿。<br />\n<br />\n同時，本畫亦是畫家最具代表性的藝術豐碑：其不僅被常玉選用於最後一次個展的邀請函封面，更常見於藝術家油畫全集及其他重要出版，誠為經典中之經典。<br />\n<br />\n在此畫背後，常玉在畫作上落款、標年代，並寫下這句話：「如果在當其時不遭窮困，勤於作畫，不致等到今日始成，則早到成熟期矣，萬歎。特此作記，時在一九六五四月。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">樓主呢幅可能會破二億 </span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fffca073cb1500f0d523132e6ca51200ccced26","tid":2246144,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"改良版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntyXNX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntyXNX8.png&h=71676bcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3412cb0d2138beba040866e8e3e517d0bc10aae1","tid":2246144,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fffca073cb1500f0d523132e6ca51200ccced26","tid":2246144,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"改良版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntyXNX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntyXNX8.png&h=71676bcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b140a7313e8a52e0eb4185fc27df5daf20b10f","tid":2246144,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"男人腳 要真腳唔要畫<br />\n<br />\n謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785f77dde3b744a3e3f41e8e0e5626b1641b38d7","tid":2246144,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89b140a7313e8a52e0eb4185fc27df5daf20b10f","tid":2246144,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"男人腳 要真腳唔要畫<br />\n<br />\n謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"自己google搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1502065d00cdecb3d903d338db3055622e13e6","tid":2246144,"uid":36116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T18:30:16.000Z","msg":"啲上色好有袁生style"},{"pid":"e224b30dac27420314e4f52ff002b44f1f3f1805","tid":2246144,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T19:12:06.000Z","msg":"#1 陰影修正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OF5OVka.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOF5OVka.png&h=9d2154d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55105da873219